article.description: — Japhet Medor had 16 points in UTSA's 61-56 victory over Texas State on Thursday.
article.headline: Medor scores 16, UTSA downs Texas State 61-56
article.linkText: Medor scores 16, UTSA downs Texas State 61-56
article.story: SAN ANTONIO -- — Japhet Medor had 16 points in UTSA's 61-56 victory over Texas State on Thursday. Medor added five rebounds for the Roadrunners (3-1). John Buggs III scored 13 points while going 5 of 8 (3 for 5 from distance), and added eight rebounds. Jacob Germany finished 5 of 14 from the field to finish with 12 points. The Bobcats (2-2) were led in scoring by Tyler Morgan, who finished with 20 points and seven rebounds. Mason Harrell added 20 points and three steals for Texas State. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
